  Locus:
    Page: 174
By: St Augustine
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Volition, Obedience and Conformity=Intention
---
All consult Thee (O Truth) on what they will, though they hear not
always what they will. He is Thy best servant, who looks not so much
to hear that from Thee, which himself willeth; as rather to will that,
which from Thee he heareth.
